race.comment: AUSSIE MOSS (1) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing sixth (30.31) in a Grade 5 FIN at Sandown. Drifted back and never in it from the wide draw. Got the money at his only try from this box. Can atone. SPRINGER'S BOY (7) beaten last start over the 450m at Shepparton but finished in the minors in a sharp 25.35. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. BREAKDOWN (2) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at The Meadows the following run. Rates a winning chance on best. NOAH'S BEST (3) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.
